column19: Nest hatched on 7-21-15, excavated on 7-24-15.  Possible that this nest hatched early (day 51 for May nest!) because it was relocated to a high, dry location?!  111 egg shells, 12 unhatched eggs (8 undeveloped, 4 pipped dead).  One live hatchling had "shoulder" caught behind cable and was trapped in the nest.  Nothing observed to account for erratic (active) graph for this nest.
